Round_Lot_Trend_Insight.insight_details: Check for any non-standard 'Round Lot Size'. Identify unusual trading volumes that could signify market anomalies.

relation_columns.Round Lot Size: Numeric column representing the standard trading unit (usually 100 shares). Important for trading operations and transaction cost analysis. Domain Relevance: critical for market trading cost evaluation.

relations.Round_Lot_Trend: Check for any non-standard 'Round Lot Size'. OUTLIER detection using IQR may identify unusual trading volumes that could signify market anomalies.

sql_results_pair.sql_query: SELECT "Round Lot Size", COUNT(*) AS frequency FROM data GROUP BY "Round Lot Size" ORDER BY frequency DESC LIMIT 5

WITH data_stats AS (SELECT AVG("Round Lot Size") AS avg, (MAX("Round Lot Size") - MIN("Round Lot Size")) / 2 AS iqr_range FROM data) SELECT "Round Lot Size" FROM data, data_stats WHERE "Round Lot Size" < (avg - iqr_range) OR "Round Lot Size" > (avg + iqr_range) ORDER BY "Round Lot Size" DESC LIMIT 5
